unico 1.0.2 (March 29, 2012)
----------------------------

* Updated to work with Gtk+ 3.4.0.

* Fixed one memory leak.

* Allow using a texture for the resize grip.


unico 1.0.1 (September 1, 2011)
-------------------------------

* Some tweaks for the GtkSpinButton.

Bugs fixed:
 833958 gtk_render_line doesn't work if y0 == y1 or x1 == x0


unico 1.0 (August 10, 2011)
---------------------------

* First public release.
